com.linkedin.pegasus2avro.dataset.ViewPr.formattedViewLogic:
WITH __dbt__CTE__customer_details AS (
  SELECT
    c.customer_id,
    c.first_name || ' ' || c.last_name AS "full_name",
    c.email,
    a.address,
    m.city,
    a.postal_code,
    a.phone
  FROM "pagila"."public"."customer" AS c
  LEFT OUTER JOIN "pagila"."public"."address" AS a
    ON c.address_id = a.address_id
  LEFT OUTER JOIN "pagila"."public"."city" AS m
    ON a.city_id = m.city_id
)
SELECT
  pbc.billing_month,
  pbc.customer_id,
  pbc.amount,
  cust.email
FROM "pagila"."dbt_postgres"."payments_by_customer_by_month" AS pbc
LEFT OUTER JOIN __dbt__CTE__customer_details AS cust
  ON pbc.customer_id = cust.customer_id
ORDER BY
  pbc.billing_month
